A man has been arrested for allegedly raping his 11-year-old granddaughter in Dobsonville, Gauteng police said today. The girl was washing dishes last night when the 67-year-old called her to their garage where he fondled and raped her, Warrant Officer Kay Makhubela said. Her parents were not there at the time.  24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.  